trans-unit.source: The `Click` event passes an <xref:System.EventArgs> to its event handler.
trans-unit.target: Den `Click` hendelsen sender en <xref:System.EventArgs>til hendelsesbehandlingen.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Therefore it only indicates that a click has occurred.
trans-unit.target: Derfor bare indikerer at det har oppstått et klikk.

trans-unit.source: If you need more specific mouse information (button, number of clicks, wheel rotation, or location), use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick> event.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du trenger mer spesifikke musen informasjon (knappen, antall Klikk, hjulet rotasjon eller plassering), kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick>

trans-unit.source: However, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick> event will not be raised if the click is caused by action other than that of the mouse, such as pressing the ENTER key.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick>vil ikke starter hendelsen hvis Klikk skyldes handling enn med musen, for eksempel å trykke ENTER-tasten.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.MouseClick>

trans-unit.source: A double-click is determined by the mouse settings of the user's operating system.
trans-unit.target: Dobbeltklikk bestemmes av innstillinger for mus av brukerens operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: The user can set the time between clicks of a mouse button that should be considered a double-click instead of two clicks.
trans-unit.target: Brukeren kan angi tiden mellom Klikk museklikk som Dobbeltklikk i stedet for to Klikk.

trans-unit.source: The `Click` event is raised every time that a control is double-clicked.
trans-unit.target: Den `Click` denne hendelsen oppstår hver gang en kontroll dobbeltklikker.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you have event handlers for the `Click` and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick> events of a [control](ms-help://MS.VSCC.v90/MS.MSDNQTR.v90.en/fxref_system.windows.forms/html/6569d671-0a28-7b3f-dbb8-90c3d272b6e2.htm), the `Click` and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick> events are raised when the control is double-clicked and both methods are called.
trans-unit.target: Hvis for eksempel, du har hendelsesbehandling for den `Click` og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick>hendelser i en [kontrollen](ms-help://MS.VSCC.v90/MS.MSDNQTR.v90.en/fxref_system.windows.forms/html/6569d671-0a28-7b3f-dbb8-90c3d272b6e2.htm), `Click` og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick>hendelser registreres når kontrollen er dobbeltklikker og begge metodene kalles.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick>

trans-unit.source: If a control is double-clicked and that control does not support the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick> event, the `Click` event might be raised two times.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en kontroll er dobbeltklikker og at kontrollen ikke støtter den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick>hendelsen den `Click` hendelsen kan opp to ganger.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.DoubleClick>

trans-unit.source: The `Layout` event occurs when child controls are added or removed, when the bounds of the control changes, and when other changes occur that can affect the layout of the control.
trans-unit.target: Den `Layout` hendelsen oppstår når underordnede kontroller legges til eller fjernes når grensene for kontrollen endres, og når det oppstår andre endringer som kan påvirke oppsettet for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The layout event can be suppressed by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SuspendLayout%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ResumeLayout%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen oppsettet kan undertrykkes ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SuspendLayout%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ResumeLayout%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ResumeLayout%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SuspendLayout%2A>

trans-unit.source: Suspending layout enables you to perform multiple actions on a control without having to perform a layout for each change.
trans-unit.target: Avbrytes oppsettet kan du utføre flere handlinger på en kontroll uten å måtte utføre en oppsettet for hver endring.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you resize and move a control, each operation would raise a `Layout` event.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du endrer størrelse på og flytte en kontroll, hver operasjon vil utløse en `Layout` hendelsen.
